    <footer class="bg-black/20 py-8 text-center">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <p class="text-blue-300">© <span id="year"></span> Professional Tester & IT Business Analyst Portfolio</p>
            <p class="text-blue-400/70 text-sm mt-2">Crafted with expertise in testing and business analysis</p>
